from sisypho.corelib.os_utils import open_app, click, type

def run() -> None:
    try:
        # Open Google Chrome
        open_app("Google Chrome")

        # Click on the "New Tab" button
        click(app_name="Google Chrome", element_descriptor="AXWindow[{{\"index\":0}}] > AXGroup[{{\"index\":0}}] > AXButton[{{\"label\":\"New Tab\"}}]", is_right_click=False, is_double_click=False, duration=100)

        # Type 'Hello World' in the new tab
        type(app_name="Google Chrome", text="Hello World")

    except Exception as e:
        print(f"An error occurred: {e}")
